.name
MainActor
.author
Markus Moenig
.type
Animation Package
.short
a modular animation package
.description
MainActor is a modular animation package which is able to
create/edit/time/play animations (of any size) of the provided
animation modules. Modules included in this release : 
IFF-Anim5/7/8/Brush, FLI, FLC, DL. You also have a great number of
functions for animation proccessing. MainActor is also able to read
and write Picture Modules : IFF, PCX, GIF, WB-ICON.
Support for the Picasso-II, Retina and Merlin card is integrated.
